Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.65,0:03:38.85,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 我正在试着让它保持稳定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.85,0:03:40.89,English,,0,0,0,,I mean I'm really working on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.85,0:03:40.89,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我的意思是我正在做这件事
