Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.01,0:04:09.97,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.97,0:04:11.14,English,,0,0,0,,- Up it comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.97,0:04:11.14,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.35,0:04:14.48,English,,0,0,0,,- [Derek] We're going to try a few more experiments,
