Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.75,0:04:28.68,English,,0,0,0,,gravity pulling it down and air resistance to the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.75,0:04:28.68,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.68,0:04:32.97,English,,0,0,0,,When flying along at constant speed, these forces must be perfectly balanced
